{"tid":749411,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 巴東牛肉 ＆甜醬油炸黃豆餅","createTime":"2018-07-20T04:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T07:04:05.000Z","uid":30742,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8799b24ef52363d98374f098d02ca8819bda1c26","tid":749411,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/120741_943fbd6becc28736e3958a38e4a82926.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F120741_943fbd6becc28736e3958a38e4a82926.jpg&h=a6755859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/120748_55803a4cf70e0f9d3145025abe7b3492.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F120748_55803a4cf70e0f9d3145025abe7b3492.jpg&h=d978dfa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴東牛肉 Beef Rendang<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YmvleyBJy6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYmvleyBJy6s&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w08mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c6b6b2c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YmvleyBJy6s</a><br />\n甜醬油炸黃豆餅 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6VNeW2OMsHM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6VNeW2OMsHM&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w08mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d522c703\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6VNeW2OMsHM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被你地撩起左我對黃豆餅的興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又無理由齋黃豆餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起印尼菜，就想整下巴東牛肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特登走左去旺角街市買料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個係完全無水無上湯，只落椰奶既巴東牛肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n味道相當濃郁，煮好後放一晚再食，更正！<br />\n印尼菜一盤盤好多唔同料真係好豐富，食起上黎都開心d！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜 <br />\n巴東牛肉 Beef Rendang <br />\n<a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/07/beef-rendang.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F07%2Fbeef-rendang.html&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w08mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7ac76a10\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/07/beef-rendang.html</a><br />\n<br />\n甜醬油炸黃豆餅 tempeh <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/07/tempeh.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F07%2Ftempeh.html&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w08mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=bc5d393d\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/07/tempeh.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w08mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=e4eee776\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w08mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=67291d01\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"htt